Suggests: hp-wmi-omen-dkms
Description: Fan control for HP Omen Max, Victus and Omen laptops (CLI + GUI)
 CLI and GUI to control fan speed on supported HP Omen and Victus laptops
 on Linux. Install hp-wmi-omen-dkms for persistent patched driver across
 kernel updates, or use "omen-fan-control install-patch permanent" from
 this package.
